Geographic Codes 1.4.0

	* Add support for 'use_label' on GeoAddressFormInputs.
	* Failsafe logic if the province check from an IP doesn't find a valid match.
	* Include the alt tag for {geoiplookup}.
	* Documentation cleanup.
	-- Charlie Powell <charlie@eval.bz>  Wed, 28 May 2014 19:41:18 -0400

