Geographic Codes 1.2.0

	* minimalect shouldn't hide the default option on selects
	* Fancy checkboxes and radios. Fully accessible and degrades nicely
	* Completely overhaul the form styling and templates on Core.
	* Switch to the bulk insert method now that Core supports it.
	* Textual/Comment change on the geoaddressforminput label input.
	* New methods for GeoAddressModel, isBlank and getCPPFormatted (aka, getCSZFormatted).
	* Add label to GeoAddress models and the respective UI.
	* Documentation change, @copyright.
	-- Charlie Powell <charlie@eval.bz>  Sat, 22 Mar 2014 14:58:00 -0400

